<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='654240' id='t-654240'>And then the whole room was clapping.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='662285' id='t-662285'>This is the moment
that I live for in lighting.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665395' id='t-665395'>The moment where it all comes together</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='667582' id='t-667582'>and we get a world that we can believe in.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:21
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670718' id='t-670718'>We use math, science and code
to create these amazing worlds.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='675030' id='t-675030'>We use storytelling and art
to bring them to life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='678440' id='t-678440'>It's this interweaving of art and science</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='682475' id='t-682475'>that elevates the world
to a place of wonder,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686162' id='t-686162'>a place with soul,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='687819' id='t-687819'>a place we can believe in,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690262' id='t-690262'>a place where the things
you imagine can become real --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695071' id='t-695071'>and a world where a girl suddenly realizes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698307' id='t-698307'>not only is she a scientist,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='700491' id='t-700491'>but also an artist.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702544' id='t-702544'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='703719' id='t-703719'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
